title: Chests
info: Chests are storage items that each hold up to 40 item stacks in rows of 10×4    / 5×8 / 5×4 (only 20 item stacks) . Chests can be freed with any pickaxe or drill, but only when empty. It is impossible to destroy the blocks underneath a placed chest that contains items.
